info.name: PeopleMover (WDW) icon bar - small
info.description: Walt Disney World's PeopleMover as your tumblr icon bar - now updated with the new "Discover" icon
info.additionalInfo:
There used to be two WDW PeopleMover styles, one for those with Xkit and one for those without. I have replaced them with a single style that will work either way.

--NOTE: While this style includes icons for Settings, Help, and Log Out, those are currently hidden with the new tumblr drop-down menu for those functions. I have left them in the theme anyway in case I ever find a way to undo the drop-down menu.
